UNGQONGQOSHE wezeMpilo kuleli uDkt Zweli Mkhize usezwakalise ukukhathazelka ngokunyuka kwesibalo sabantu abaneCovid-19 esifundazweni iWestern Cape. Ngokwezibalo ezimenyenzelwe uMnyango wezeMpilo ngeSonto isibalo sabantu abahaqekile kuleli sinyukele ku-15 515 kanti isibalo sabashonile sinyukele ku-264 kulandela ukushona kwabanye abathathu. Sekuhlolwe abantu abawu-460 873 kuleli.  As of today, the total number of confirmed #COVID19 cases in South Africa is 15 515, the total number of deaths is 264 and the total recoveries is 7006. pic.twitter.com/MH3KJqKSnw #COVID19SouthAfrica Statistics as at 17 May 2020. pic.twitter.com/ivAa02sxXw  UMkhize uthe sebekuqaphile ukuthi kubantu abashonile, abawu-148 abesilisa, abawu-116 abesifazane. Sekushone abantu abawu-149 eWestern Cape, KwaZulu-Natal sekushone abawu-45, e-Eastern Cape sekushone abawu-35 kanti eGauteng kusashone abawu-25. Okuzothokozelwa abaningi nokho ukunyuka kwesibalo sabantu asebesindile kuleli gciwane kuleli njengoba sebewu-7 006. Emhlabeni jikelele babalelwa ngaphezulu kuka-1.8 million abantu asebesindile kuleli gciwane eselihaqe abangaphezulu kuka-4.7 million. #ListenToTheExpertIt is important that we adhere to the conditions of the lockdown, says Professor Khangelani Zuma of the HSRC. pic.twitter.com/HdCLkHjEKi